 around any construction site.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium;\">Large, threaded top fill-port and bottom drain plugs make it easy to load and unload with sand or water ballast. Bright colors improve safety and are easier to see than concrete or wood.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium;\">All SAFEGUARD Plastic water barriers filled Barriers are rotationally molded to assure durability and resistance to harsh conditions.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>"},{"attribute_code":"designcenter_image_upload_type","value":"null"},{"attribute_code":"accessories","value":"1119"},{"attribute_code":"base_type","value":"523"}]},{"id":13026,"sku":"SGB3672WTFT","name":"SGB3672WTFT","attribute_set_id":20,"price":389,"status":1,"visibility":1,"type_id":"simple","created_at":"2019-06-04 15:24:38","updated_at":"2019-06-04 15:24:38","weight":95,"extension_attributes":{"website_ids":[1,5],"category_links":[{"position":1,"category_id":"7"},{"position":1,"category_id":"11"},{"position":1,"category_id":"22"},{"position":1,"category_id":"82"},{"position":1,"category_id":"83"},{"position":1,"category_id":"84"},{"position":1,"category_id":"92"},{"position":1,"category_id":"108"},{"position":1,"category_id":"114"},{"position":1,"category_id":"185"},{"position":1,"category_id":"252"},{"position":5,"category_id":"262"},{"position":1,"category_id":"269"},{"position":15,"category_id":"271"},{"position":1,"category_id":"291"},{"position":1,"category_id":"293"},{"position":1,"category_id":"328"},{"position":1,"category_id":"329"},{"position":1,"category_id":"330"},{"position":1,"category_id":"343"},{"position":1,"category_id":"348"}]},"product_links":[],"options":[],"media_gallery_entries":[],"tier_prices":[],"custom_attributes":[{"attribute_code":"url_key","value":"sgb3672wtft"},{"attribute_code":"custom_design_from","value":"2017-08-06 10:47:50"},{"attribute_code":"short_description","value":"The Sonco SafeGuard water filled traffic barrier is pe