t your specific needs<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">**Compatible with plain and custom printed barricade covers**<\/span><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<hr \/>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Amazing discounts for bulk orders<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">Take advantage of our temporary low price for early access purchases and save even more when purchasing barriers in large quantities early.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">Early Access Price! Promotion ends soon.<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">Special pricing for purchases above 100 units<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">Distribution across the US via our strategically placed warehouses to deliver our products the most economical way and allow huge savings on freight costs regardless of your location in the country!<\/span><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<div><\/div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">Contact us today to discuss your crowd control needs with a dedicated account manager. We&rsquo;ll provide you with a free quote in no time!<\/span><\/div>"},{"attribute_code":"finish","value":"342"},{"attribute_code":"color","value":"52"},{"attribute_code":"designcenter_image_upload_type","value":"null"}]},{"id":12975,"sku":"PBWB600","name":"Heavy Duty Steel Barricades - Truckload Bundle","attribute_set_id":19,"price":80,"status":2,"visibility":4,"type_id":"simple","created_at":"2019-02-28 14:39:28","updated_at":"2019-05-06 03:50:52","weight":55,"extension_attributes":{"website_ids":[1,5],"category_links":[{"position":1,"category_id":"2"},{"position":1,"category_id":"11"},{"position":1,"category_id":"39"},{"position":1,"category_id":"50"},{"position":1,"category_id":"123"},{"position":1,"category_id":"252"},{"position":0,"category_id":"262"},{