www.soncocrowdcontrol.com\/barricades\/stage-barriers\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">here.<\/span><\/a> Easy to clean up due to holes in the floors which helps minimize the effect of spills.<\/span><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">Compact Storage<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #000000;\">All Crowd Control Barricade folds flat for easy and compact storage. Stackable <a href=\"https:\/\/www.soncocrowdcontrol.com\/catalog\/product\/view\/id\/9090\/s\/stage-barrier-cart\/category\/270\/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Barricade Cart<\/span><\/a> is also available for easy transport with a simple box truck or trailer and moving the barriers around the event site.<\/span><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>"},{"attribute_code":"color","value":"811"},{"attribute_code":"designcenter_image_upload_type","value":"null"}]}';